<i>noun</i>: 손가락질 [손까락찔] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>손가락질 [손까락찔]</dt><br>
<dd>1. finger-pointing; pointing</dd><br>
<dd>손가락으로 무엇을 가리키는 행동.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of indicating something with a finger.</dd><br>
<dd>2. criticism</dd><br>
<dd>남을 흉보는 행동.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of finding fault with others.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>